content.rendered:
Directed by Thiagarajan Kumararaja

Written by Thiagarajan Kumararaja. Nalan Kumarasamy. Mysskin. Sekar Neelan

Cast Vijay Sethupathi (Shilpa). Fahadh Faasil (Mugil). Samantha Ruth Prabhu (Vaembu (as Samantha Akkineni)). Ramya Krishnan (Leela). Mysskin (Arputham (as Myshkin)). Bagavathi Perumal (Berlin (as Bucks)). Gayathrie (Jyothi). Ashwanth Ashokkumar (Raasu Kutti). Jayanth (Mohan). Mirnalini Ravi (Alien). Noble (Vasanth). Vijay Ram (Gaaji Balaji). Abdul Jabbar (Thooyavan). Naveen (Soori). Manushyaputhiran (Doctor in a Movie). Rengarajan Rajagopalan (Vaembu’s Lover). Kavin Jay Balaji (Idi Ameen) . Abdool Lee (Doctor (as Abdool)). Noble (Mutta puffs). Vivek Raju (School Boy’s Father)

Languages Tamil

Producers S.D. Ezhilmathy. Thiagarajan Kumararaja. Sathyaraj Natarajan

Production Tyler Durden and Kino Fis. East West Dream Works Entertainmen. Alchemy Vision Work
